casebody.data:
MONTANA POWER COMPANY v. Isobel BASKEN. No. 8205. Circuit Court of Appeals, Nintli Circuit. June 10, 1936. Gunn, Rasch, Hall & Gunn, of Helena, Mont.,’ and' D. M. Kelly, John V. Dwyer, and John E. Corette, Jr., all of Butte, Mont., for appellant. Wellington D. Rankin and Arthur P. Acher, both of Helena, Mont., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
